headline.print_headline: Nadal to Face Local Hope Tomic in Australian Open
headline.main: Nadal to Face Local Hope Tomic in Australian Open

lead_paragraph: World number one Rafal Nadal will play local hope Bernard Tomic in the first round of the Australian Open as he bids for a 14th grand slam title.
